743
01:10:02,344 --> 01:10:08,344
hololive 7th fes. Ridin' on Dreams
[Title: hololive 7th fes. Ridin' on Dreams]

744
01:10:08,344 --> 01:10:14,344
無料パートは終了いたしました！ご視聴ありがとうございました！
[Text: The free part has ended! Thank you for watching!]

745
01:11:24,144 --> 01:11:26,744
ねえ、君がいたからだよ
Hey, it's because you were there

746
01:11:26,744 --> 01:11:29,744
ねえ、ありがとうを何度も
Hey, I want to say "thank you" over and over

747
01:11:29,744 --> 01:11:33,344
今すぐに伝えたいんだ
I want to tell you right now

748
01:11:33,344 --> 01:11:36,344
さあ乗り込もう!
Come on, let's hop on!

749
01:11:36,344 --> 01:11:39,744
Ridin' on Dreams Yeah!!

750
01:11:39,744 --> 01:11:43,344
Wow oh oh…

751
01:11:43,344 --> 01:11:45,344
Hey!! (Hey!!)

752
01:11:45,344 --> 01:11:47,344
Hey!! (Hey!!)

753
01:11:47,344 --> 01:11:50,144
Yeah!!

754
01:11:50,644 --> 01:11:53,644
あぁ 小さな夢から
Ah, from a small dream

755
01:11:53,644 --> 01:11:56,744
想像できないような
To something I could never have imagined

756
01:11:56,744 --> 01:11:59,944
想いになったんだ
My feelings have grown so much

757
01:11:59,944 --> 01:12:03,344
わくわく止まらない!
My excitement won't stop!

758
01:12:03,344 --> 01:12:06,944
何度迷ったって僕ら
No matter how many times we get lost

759
01:12:06,944 --> 01:12:10,144
絆が舵になる
Our bond becomes the rudder

760
01:12:10,144 --> 01:12:13,544
ちょっとの不安だってさ
Even a little bit of anxiety

761
01:12:13,544 --> 01:12:16,844
吹き飛ばせちゃうんだよ
We can blow it all away

762
01:12:16,844 --> 01:12:20,144
果てない旅路を今
Now, on this endless journey

763
01:12:20,144 --> 01:12:23,544
漕いでる途中に困難もあるでしょう
There will be difficulties while we're rowing

764
01:12:23,544 --> 01:12:26,844
それも力に変えて
Let's turn those into strength too

765
01:12:26,844 --> 01:12:29,344
一緒に進むんだよ!
And move forward together!

